%% JSON CSRF:

1) change the content Type
    from: application/json   to: text/plain
   
    If no error in the response then send JSON data as
    
    <form action="URL" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
      <input type="text" name='{//// JSON ///}' />
      <input type="submit" name="submit" />
    </form>


2) If first not works:
    
    Change the content type: application/X-www-form-urlencoded
    and send the values as HTML tags
